"8WRGND24.1A1G" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
Per the FCC test report, the test program for the SoC is '''MT7620QA.exe'''. :The WiSoC is presumed to be a '''MediaTek''' MT7620A. It is not visible (or rather, it's covered) in the FCC photos.
Default settings (including the SSID patterns) are per the FCC sample label/manual.
The power adapter shown in the FCC external photos is an '''AMIGO''' AMS9-1201000FC2 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 12VDC, 1.0A).
